@node intro "Introduction"

	Wiseman 1.0 introduction

	
	Wiseman is a program for viewing fortune cookies.
	Fortune cookies are wise words and quotes of famous
	people. This program scans trough a file with quotes
	and picks a random quote, and displays it.
@endnode


